\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 John Percy Partridge, 11 King }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15077704\charrsid15482426 George}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
