\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Married twice.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Could you give me the year of your marriage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 1926. That was the first one. 1951, the second one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 And your year of birth?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 1902.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 And the place you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Camden Town.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Do you know the address?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Kings Road I believe it was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 How many years did you live in Kings Road, Camden Town?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Myself? Couple of year that's all. Moved as a baby, don't remember it at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Whereabouts did you go from there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Hackney.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 What was your address in Hackney?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Maddley Street.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 How long did you live in that house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 I say roughly - to my memory - six or seven years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 So you'd be about eight or nine when you moved from Mabberley Street?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Where did you go from there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Went to }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15077704\charrsid15482426 Bartlett}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426  Street, quite a little - few turnings away, same locality.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 How long did you stay in that one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Oh 'til I was married. Eighteen year I suppose roughly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Do you remember why your family made these moves?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 No, I wouldn't know, I was too young.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 How many brothers and sisters did you have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Two brothers, two sisters.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Can you tell me their ages?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Now or ....?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 The order they came in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 
Yes. Eldest one, eldest brothers, he's eighty. The second brother, he got killed in war, he'd be about seventy-eight. Sister seventy-four. Another sister - seventy. Then myself. I was the baby.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Have you any idea how old your father was when you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 When I was born? Thirty-one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Where did he come from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 I wouldn't know. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 What was his occupation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 He was a carpenter.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Had he been a carpenter all his life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 As far as I know, yes. 'Cos remember I was quite a baby - I never knew him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 He died when you were quite young did he?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Yes, when I was about three year old.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Do you know whether he did any casual or part time jobs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 No, I don't think so. Regular employment.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 How old was your mother when you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 I should think about thirty-two.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Where did she come from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Well London as far as I know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Did she have any jobs before she was married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 I believe she was in service.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Did she work after she was married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 After she became a widow, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 What did she do then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 She worked in a - collar factory I believe, ironing or - sewing collars, something to do with the shirt trade, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Did she carry on with that all her life? Did she do anything else afterwards?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 No, as far as I know that's all she done, she might have done one or two other jobs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Do you know what sort of hours she worked at this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 No, I wouldn't know, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 But it was full time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Yes. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Who looked after you children while your mother was at work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Well we just went to school you know, nobody looked after us, we was 11 school age.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Being the youngest you'd have the older ones?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Ones just to - keep an eye on me, yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 I think we'll talk about the second house you were in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Yes. Yes. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 How many rooms were there in that house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Four rooms and a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15077704\charrsid15482426 box room}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 , what we used to call a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15077704\charrsid15482426 box room}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 , small room.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Was that a front room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Yes, front room, kitchen, scullery and two bedrooms. Two main bedrooms.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Did anyone else besides your mother and brothers and sisters live in the house, any relatives or lodgers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Well, I think automatically as we all got married we all lived in one room for a time 'til we got our own places.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 But there wasn't anyone outside the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 No. Family. No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Did your mother ever pay anyone to help - her in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Was the washing done at home or sent out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Done at home. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Did your mother make any of your clothes at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 No, not }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4022478\charrsid15482426 as}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426  far as I remember. She may have made the girls things, odds and ends but nothing - on a scale.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Were your clothes new or secondhand?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Mostly secondhand.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Where were they bought?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 
Well, local - what we called a rag and - people, you know, used to have stalls and - you used to go down there and buy a pair of trousers for - a bob or so. Secondhand.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Were these like street markets or were they shops?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 
Well they was houses turned into shops, one in particular I remember used to have - secondhand clothes outside. Used to go and buy a pair of trousers for a shilling or something like that. Very seldom had new clothes in them days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 These weren't the pawnshops though?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 No, not the pawnshops, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Was there any special time for buying clothes or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 No. No, you just went - nearly all day. I should say Sunday morning was pretty popular. More people about and she had the stall out in
 front of her house and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 So you had Sunday opening for shops?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Yes, oh yes, nearly all shops opened.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Were shoes new or secondhand?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 No, very seldom. Generally secondhand shoes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 As children did you have any tasks to carry out in the home at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 
Well just - cleaning the silver and - things like that. In fact myself, I used to go to a relation and do a bit of cleaning used to get a few coppers you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 You had relatives living near?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Yes, I used to go and clean their knives and forks, with the old brick dust and whitening you know. Get tuppence or threepence.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Did you continue these sort of tasks after you had left school or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 No. No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 This was just to give you a bit of pocket money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Yes, that's right, a few coppers for spending.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Were you expected to go to bed at a certain time in your schooldays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Do you remember what your bedtime was?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 I should say roughly seven-ish. Perhaps eight as we got a little bit older. Pretty strict on that. Mother was, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Did mother or anyone else put you to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Not as far as I remember, not when I - was old enough you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Did you share a bedroom or bed with anyone?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 I didn't share a bedroom but - I used to sl
eep in the kitchen, and - the older ones had to go out the room while I undressed because I didn't have a bedroom for me. That was when I was, what - eleven upwards you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 What were the sleeping arrangements?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Well, you see, the eldest brother
 was married then and he had the front room, him and his wife, for perhaps a year, two years, and nearly everyone had that and - I - I being the youngest and the boy after the two girls, I was just - had to put up with a bed in - what we called the kitche
n at the time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 So your mother would have one of the rooms?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Yes. - Yes. Well the front room downstairs - would be the - the girls room you see. Then we had that}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid15482426  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4022478\charrsid15482426 little}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426  off room for the other boy and I used to - bed down in the kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 So you more or less had to wait until everyone went to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 
Well, mostly they went out of the room while I got into bed when I was young and then they'd come back. I mean often I'd be in bed and they're having their supper. Yes. Yes. I had to go to bed, I 
wasn't allowed to stop up 'til - ten or eleven you know, I had to go to bed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 So you didn't get away with anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 No. No. No, although she was a widow she kept us - well in hand you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 What room did you bath in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 In the kitchen, in front of the fire.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 How often would this happen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Once a week. Friday or Saturday night, whatever was convenient.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 When did you have clean clothes?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 At that time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Where did the family have their meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 In the kitchen. Well what we called the kitchen. Well I mean they're called dining rooms now. For us }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid15077704\charrsid15482426 Londoners}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426  they - they're kitchens.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Were there any occasions when you ate in another room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 No, very seldom. As I say there was beds is in every room. If we had a - a bi
rthday or something like that we'd probably take the bed down - in the front room and have a little }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15077704\charrsid15482426 tea party}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 
 or something that, but generally we spent our lives in the kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 What sort of cooking equipment did you have in that house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Gas stove.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 What time was breakfast eaten?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 
Well, those that went to work, I should say between half past seven and eight, but - I used to have to go out to breakfast because - I was - what they call on free meals at the time, mother being a widow - with 
five children, and I used to go out to a church round the corner and have me breakfast and also me dinner. And I used to go there quarter past eight, half past eight.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Do you remember who provided this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Well I think it was a - under the L.C.C. th
en. Yes. You had to be very poor to get it, as I say, there was five of us, and no father you see. And for a time mother didn't go to work so - we had it pretty tough. Yes. But - good meals I must say that. Breakfast was very good you know. In fact the pl
ace we went to is called Eden Mission, it's still there, it's quite a big - well known place in Hackney Wick you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Did you eat your breakfast and dinner there for most of your childhood?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 As far as I can remember in me teens, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 How about your evening meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 
Used to have it at home. Bread and dripping or toast. Probably have a little bit of fish or - off the oldest brother's plate, something like you know, he was at work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 How did the others manage for their first meal, do you know what they used to have?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 
Well the other girl used to come with me to the free meals and the others used to have - just ordinary plain food you know. The eldest son being at work, he had a luxury or two which - probably we had a little bit of if h
e could spare it or if he felt in a good mood.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Did you have anything different to eat on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Oh yes, I'd say we - probably have egg for breakfast and - roast, in fact we always had a roast dinner times. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 These free meals you and your sister had?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Meals. Yes. I had. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 How many days a week did you have these?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Schooldays, five days, only five days, Saturday and Sunday is at home, yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 What sort of thing would you have for a midday meal while you were at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 When I was at home, well - meat puddings, stew, sausages, anything cheap you know like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Would you have your main meal of the day at midday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12478316 JP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 Midday, yes.
