\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15077704\charrsid15482426 She\rquote d}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426  try and persuade you?
