Oh respect her. Be polite. Do as you were told, near enough we done it because we were brought up to do it. I can't remember ever getting beatings, we just automatically - brought up that way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9006662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10166979\charrsid15482426 You can't remember being punished?
